{"tid":871002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【猛男送餐】英國半裸肌肉男赴安老院送餐 老友記笑逐顏開","createTime":"2018-10-21T14:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T23:19:29.000Z","uid":122,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"79b41bf55fbf321af497af4248ecc5792593a886","tid":871002,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/17/76/10177651_976885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F17%2F76%2F10177651_976885.jpg&h=d43e916d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/17/76/10177652_707688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F17%2F76%2F10177652_707688.jpg&h=0f7fe489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/17/76/10177653_212154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F17%2F76%2F10177653_212154.jpg&h=0565853e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國埃塞克斯郡(Essex)科爾切斯特(Colchester)一間安老院，為打破沈悶的院社氣氛，日前特別安排兩名半裸猛男為院內婆婆送餐，並與院友大玩遊戲。老友記見到猛男，個個笑逐顏開。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，兩位身材健碩的猛男，早前僅穿一條紅色圍巾，便前往Milton Care Lodge養老院送餐。當兩名猛男現身時，現場11名婆婆顯得極為興奮。有婆婆更在用餐期間，更多手嘗試解下猛男的圍裙帶，場面搞笑。晚餐過後，猛男更與婆婆們玩遊戲，令一眾老友記High爆。<br />\n<br />\n院社中最年長的99歲婆婆Doll Jenkins表示，無論年紀有多大，看見猛男都會令人開心，希望100歲生日時仍能看到他們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女權西 where are u"},{"pid":"c491c64225242f87047eec572229b0583bcba270","tid":871002,"uid":818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bac4b8c4eb89952a0a42981cb0704a620afea3f","tid":871002,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"d82f7495afc8ae488f62078566551ff81f918580","tid":871002,"uid":9286,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14: